                        <ul class="small">
                            <li> What is a question you have about sex that you would  like to learn about from your peers?
                            <li> Did you have any formal sexual education in school? What was your experience like? Is there a memory you'd like to share? If you have not had formal sex education before, what has sex education meant to you in your life?
                            <li> What does a safer learning environment for learning about sex look like for you?
                            <li> Why are you interested in studying at SFPC: Sex Ed? Why now?
                        </ul>

                        <BR><BR>

                        <p class="small">
                          By applying for the program, you are invited to respond to and contribute questions that may appear on this column. Applications open until July 1, 2022.
                        </p>
                        <span class="responses">
