                      <h2>About SFPC: Sex Ed</h2>
                      <p class="small">
                        SFPC: Sex Ed is a pleasure and queer centered experiment in shared study and epistemic empowerment. This program is a direct response to creating the kinds of educational spaces we never had, but always sought. Everyone deserves platonic and friendly spaces to learn and explore sexuality and pleasure informed by cultural understandings of sex, gender, class and race and how our identities relate to sexual desires, practices and kink.
                        <a href="https://sfpc.study/sessions/sex-ed">More...</a>

                      </p>



